======================================================
 Time Schedule
======================================================
 Time precision patch is 1e-05

=====|    Phase I     |===============================
-----. CPM .------------------------------------
  + 0.3 => CPM [A,prot] -> [cell.center,cell.length,cell.surface,cell.type,cell.volume]
-----. Reactions .------------------------------------
  + 0.01 => System [WavePinning with Inhibitor] [H,K,T,delta,gamma,k_0,k_1,n,s,s_1] -> [A,B,H,P2,P3,rate1]
  + 0.01 => System [cell.surface] -> [T]

=====|    Phase II    |===============================
-----. Reporters and Instantaneous Processes.---------
  + 0.01 => Mapper [Polarity extraction from membrane] [A,cell.center] -> [p]
  + 0.3 => Protrusion [prot] -> [prot]
  + 0.01 => Event [p.phi,time,ts2] -> [ts3]
  + -1 => Mapper [Polarity extraction from membrane] [U,cell.center] -> [p1]
  + 0.3 => Mapper [Sensing the field] [U,cell.center] -> [s]

=====|    Phase III   |===============================
-----. Analysis .-------------------------------------
  + 10 => Gnuplotter [A,U,p] 
  + 1 => CellTracker [cell.center] 
  + 10 => Logger [A,B,H,P3,m.phi,p.phi,s] 
  + 6000 => ModelGraph [] 
  + 10 => Gnuplotter [U,cell.type] 
  + 1 => Logger [cell.center.x,cell.center.y,cell.length,cell.surface,cell.volume] 
------------------------------------------------------
